Consider the following C# snippet class available in a generic **TestBridge.dll**:


    using System;

    namespace TestBridge
    {
        public class MyClass
        {
            /// &lt;summary&gt;The method &lt;c&gt;HelloWorld&lt;/c&gt; return the &quot;Hello World!!&quot; string&lt;/summary&gt;
